---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Project One — STUDIO" page="jeu">
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:96px"><div class="wrap reveal">
    <div class="game-hero"><div class="art-bg"></div><div class="inner">
      <p class="kick mono">// action · aventure</p><h1>Project One</h1>
      <p class="tag">Le pitch en une phrase.</p>
      <div class="store-btns"><a class="btn-primary" href="#">WISHLIST STEAM</a><a class="btn-ghost" href="#">// bande-annonce</a></div>
    </div></div>
  </div></section>
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:0"><div class="wrap reveal">
    <div class="gallery"><div class="shot sh1"></div><div class="shot sh2"></div><div class="shot sh3"></div><div class="shot sh4"></div><div class="shot sh5"></div><div class="shot sh1"></div></div>
  </div></section>
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:0"><div class="wrap split">
    <div class="prose reveal">
      <p>Description du jeu. Ce qu'on y vit, l'ambiance.</p>
      <p>Ce qu'il offre que personne d'autre ne fait pareil.</p>
      <h3 style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin:14px 0 18px">// features</h3>
      <ul class="feature-list"><li>Mécanique signature.</li><li>Second pilier de gameplay.</li><li>Ce qui donne envie d'y revenir.</li><li>Mode solo / multi / co-op.</li></ul>
    </div>
    <aside class="spec reveal"><h3>// fiche technique</h3>
      <div class="spec-row"><span>Genre</span><span>Action · Aventure</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span>Plateformes</span><span>PC · Quest</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span>Sortie</span><span>2026</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span>Joueurs</span><span>1 — 4</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span>Moteur</span><span>Unity</span></div>
      <div style="margin-top:20px"><a class="btn-primary" href="#" style="display:block;text-align:center">WISHLIST</a></div>
    </aside>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
